WEBVTT

00:00:14.680 --> 00:00:15.390 line:80%
Miss Fan.

00:00:19.190 --> 00:00:20.280 line:80%
I agreed.

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:22.310 line:80%
Well, drink it while it's hot.

00:00:22.310 --> 00:00:23.560 line:80%
I mean,

00:00:24.470 --> 00:00:25.800 line:80%
I agreed to marry into

00:00:26.470 --> 00:00:27.560 line:80%
your family.

00:00:35.150 --> 00:00:35.870 line:80%
Okay.

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:38.150 line:80%
Good.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.800 line:80%
After we are married,

00:00:42.120 --> 00:00:44.760 line:80%
we'll tell others
that you married into my family.

00:00:44.760 --> 00:00:46.150 line:80%
Once the house title is transferred

00:00:46.150 --> 00:00:47.440 line:80%
and the money situation is sorted out,

00:00:47.440 --> 00:00:50.080 line:80%
I'll hire the very best doctor in town

00:00:50.120 --> 00:00:51.440 line:80%
and use the finest medicine
to treat your injuries.

00:00:51.440 --> 00:00:52.570 line:80%
After you recover,

00:00:52.650 --> 00:00:53.390 line:80%
whether you want to stay or go

00:00:53.390 --> 00:00:54.270 line:80%
is entirely up to you.

00:00:54.270 --> 00:00:57.080 line:80%
Aren't you afraid that after I leave,

00:00:57.830 --> 00:01:00.630 line:80%
your uncle will come back
to seize the house again?

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:04.179 line:80%
Once the property is in my name,

00:01:04.179 --> 00:01:05.750 line:80%
why should I be afraid of him?

00:01:05.750 --> 00:01:06.720 line:80%
Besides,

00:01:06.920 --> 00:01:08.200 line:80%
when you leave,

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:10.480 line:80%
I'll just say you've gone on a long trip.

00:01:10.540 --> 00:01:11.940 line:80%
Who would know the truth?

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:15.060 line:80%
You've thought this through.

00:01:17.440 --> 00:01:18.640 line:80%
If you decide to stay,

00:01:19.150 --> 00:01:21.010 line:80%
I'll feed you by butchering pigs.

00:01:22.110 --> 00:01:22.950 line:80%
Why?

00:01:23.390 --> 00:01:24.589 line:80%
You may not know this,

00:01:25.030 --> 00:01:27.360 line:80%
but we butchers make a lot of money.

00:01:29.230 --> 00:01:30.360 line:80%
I mean,

00:01:31.839 --> 00:01:33.390 line:80%
if I am a cripple,

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:35.800 line:80%
what would you gain from keeping me?

00:01:35.800 --> 00:01:37.529 line:80%
Because you're good-looking.

00:01:38.750 --> 00:01:40.370 line:80%
Fan Changyu,

00:01:40.670 --> 00:01:41.200 line:80%
how could you say something

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:43.110 line:80%
so heartfelt?

00:01:45.110 --> 00:01:46.510 line:80%
There are countless

00:01:46.839 --> 00:01:48.839 line:80%
good-looking people in this world.

00:01:49.750 --> 00:01:50.480 line:80%
Why me?

00:01:50.589 --> 00:01:53.200 line:80%
But the one I carried out of the snow
was you.

00:01:55.510 --> 00:01:57.940 line:80%
If you have nowhere to go
after you recover...

00:01:57.940 --> 00:01:58.870 line:80%
After I recover,

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.820 line:80%
I will leave.

00:02:01.870 --> 00:02:03.470 line:80%
I won't overstay my welcome.

00:02:09.920 --> 00:02:10.850 line:80%
That's fine too.

00:02:12.550 --> 00:02:13.620 line:80%
I'll be going now.

00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:18.480 line:80%
Miss Fan.

00:02:20.990 --> 00:02:22.080 line:80%
I will repay you

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:24.140 line:80%
for saving my life.

00:02:24.710 --> 00:02:26.550 line:80%
If you have any wish,

00:02:27.600 --> 00:02:28.390 line:80%
just say it.

00:02:30.430 --> 00:02:32.490 line:80%
I don't really have any other wishes.

00:02:33.670 --> 00:02:34.950 line:80%
I'm already very grateful that

00:02:34.950 --> 00:02:36.480 line:80%
you agreed
to pretend to marry into my family

00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:37.940 line:80%
and help me keep the house.

00:02:37.950 --> 00:02:39.760 line:80%
Pretending to marry into your family

00:02:39.760 --> 00:02:42.480 line:80%
is just my way
of repaying your kindness in taking me in.

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:44.390 line:80%
If you have any wishes,

00:02:44.670 --> 00:02:45.879 line:80%
you can dream big.

00:02:47.200 --> 00:02:48.950 line:80%
Wishes?

00:02:50.920 --> 00:02:51.990 line:80%
Dream big?

00:02:53.830 --> 00:02:55.110 line:80%
Then I'll dream big.

00:02:56.040 --> 00:02:57.920 line:80%
I want to run

00:02:57.950 --> 00:02:59.160 line:80%
my father's pigsty,

00:02:59.430 --> 00:03:01.200 line:80%
get a bigger plot of land,

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:03.830 line:80%
and keep 20 or 30 pigs.

00:03:08.270 --> 00:03:11.640 line:80%
You can... go bigger.

00:03:11.640 --> 00:03:12.760 line:80%
Then 100 pigs.

00:03:14.550 --> 00:03:15.870 line:80%
I mean,

00:03:16.670 --> 00:03:18.640 line:80%
do you have any grand life goals?

00:03:18.830 --> 00:03:21.920 line:80%
100 pigs are worth
over 100 taels of silver.

00:03:22.230 --> 00:03:24.000 line:80%
Isn't that a grand life goal?

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:24.550 line:80%
Well...

00:03:24.550 --> 00:03:25.879 line:80%
Then 200 pigs.

00:03:26.550 --> 00:03:27.710 line:80%
200 pigs?

00:03:27.710 --> 00:03:29.170 line:80%
I can't butcher that many.

00:03:31.950 --> 00:03:32.830 line:80%
Got it.

00:03:36.430 --> 00:03:38.290 line:80%
Let's make a pact with a high five.

00:03:47.820 --> 00:03:49.110 line:80%
Hello, Miss Changyu.

00:03:49.320 --> 00:03:49.950 line:80%
Hello.

00:03:58.670 --> 00:04:00.920 line:80%
-Changyu!
-Changyu!

00:04:00.920 --> 00:04:03.670 line:80%
-Changyu!
-Changyu!

00:04:04.040 --> 00:04:05.030 line:80%
Go play.

00:04:14.390 --> 00:04:14.950 line:80%
Here.

00:04:15.510 --> 00:04:16.310 line:80%
Okay.

00:04:16.670 --> 00:04:17.500 line:80%
One, two!

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:18.660 line:80%
Thank you, miss.

00:04:21.139 --> 00:04:22.350 line:80%
Alright. Here.

00:04:24.110 --> 00:04:24.750 line:80%
Mrs. Wang.

00:04:24.750 --> 00:04:25.430 line:80%
Changyu.

00:04:25.430 --> 00:04:26.480 line:80%
Wang, Zhang.

00:04:26.660 --> 00:04:35.390 line:80%
[Yaxiu Embroidery House]

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:35.670 line:80%
Ma'am,

00:04:36.310 --> 00:04:38.520 line:80%
my mother had previously reserved fabric

00:04:38.520 --> 00:04:40.530 line:80%
for my wedding clothes at your shop.

00:04:41.670 --> 00:04:42.550 line:80%
Follow me this way.

00:04:42.550 --> 00:04:42.990 line:80%
Okay.

00:04:49.430 --> 00:04:51.750 line:80%
She did reserve a batch of fabric,

00:04:51.840 --> 00:04:55.110 line:80%
just enough
for a full set of wedding clothes.

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:57.630 line:80%
Can it be made into
a groom's wedding outfit?

00:04:57.630 --> 00:04:59.360 line:80%
A groom's wedding outfit?

00:05:00.520 --> 00:05:02.520 line:80%
I knew that voice sounded familiar.

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:04.720 line:80%
Isn't this Changyu?

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:05.770 line:80%
Mrs. Chen.

00:05:06.110 --> 00:05:07.440 line:80%
I heard from Mrs. Zhao

00:05:07.470 --> 00:05:09.550 line:80%
that your family
is joining the wedding frenzy.

00:05:09.550 --> 00:05:11.450 line:80%
When is the big day?

00:05:11.550 --> 00:05:12.520 line:80%
In 7 days.

00:05:13.070 --> 00:05:14.750 line:80%
Then it might be too late

00:05:14.750 --> 00:05:16.210 line:80%
to order wedding clothes.

00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:18.310 line:80%
Upon hearing that the army
is recruiting in Chongzhou,

00:05:18.310 --> 00:05:20.230 line:80%
everyone is rushing

00:05:20.670 --> 00:05:22.520 line:80%
to get married to secure an heir.

00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:24.230 line:80%
My staff in the shop

00:05:24.230 --> 00:05:25.290 line:80%
can barely keep up.

00:05:28.310 --> 00:05:29.740 line:80%
I heard from Mrs. Zhao

00:05:29.770 --> 00:05:31.700 line:80%
that your groom is quite handsome.

00:05:32.750 --> 00:05:34.080 line:80%
I suppose so.

00:05:34.230 --> 00:05:35.630 line:80%
Anyway, I'm not at a loss.

00:05:36.310 --> 00:05:38.520 line:80%
Mrs. Chen, please speed up the work.

00:05:38.630 --> 00:05:40.280 line:80%
I'll pay you extra.

00:05:40.310 --> 00:05:41.980 line:80%
Who's asking for that?

00:05:42.190 --> 00:05:43.470 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:05:43.520 --> 00:05:44.430 line:80%
I helped your mother

00:05:44.430 --> 00:05:46.910 line:80%
pick out this fabric for the wedding clothes
and left it here.

00:05:46.910 --> 00:05:49.170 line:80%
She was looking forward to your wedding.

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:53.800 line:80%
I heard from Mrs. Zhao that the groom

00:05:53.800 --> 00:05:57.310 line:80%
is her distant relative from Chongzhou.

00:06:02.990 --> 00:06:04.800 line:80%
From Chongzhou?

00:06:05.430 --> 00:06:08.630 line:80%
Does he know whether the Marquis of Wu'an
is alive or dead?

00:06:09.430 --> 00:06:11.230 line:80%
Th-The Marquis of Wu'an is dead?

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:12.230 line:80%
Is that true?

00:06:12.230 --> 00:06:13.430 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an?

00:06:13.670 --> 00:06:16.910 line:80%
-Listen. Isn't that what people say?
-The Marquis of Wu'an really died.

00:06:16.910 --> 00:06:17.720 line:80%
He died in Chongzhou.

00:06:17.720 --> 00:06:18.430 line:80%
No remains were found.

00:06:18.430 --> 00:06:19.630 line:80%
Just like his father.

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:20.750 line:80%
Nonsense!

00:06:20.750 --> 00:06:22.230 line:80%
How could the Marquis of Wu'an be dead?

00:06:22.230 --> 00:06:23.430 line:80%
I'll slap you!

00:06:23.430 --> 00:06:25.560 line:80%
Don't you think he deserves a beating?

00:06:38.150 --> 00:06:43.470 line:80%
[Chongde Hall]

00:06:39.670 --> 00:06:40.900 line:80%
Our Great Yin

00:06:41.070 --> 00:06:43.570 line:80%
has been at war with Beijue for years.

00:06:43.959 --> 00:06:46.870 line:80%
Xie Zheng, the Marquis of Wu'an,
a hero of his generation,

00:06:46.870 --> 00:06:48.720 line:80%
ended up with no body to bury.

00:06:48.959 --> 00:06:50.910 line:80%
It is truly a tragedy for Great Yin.

00:06:51.990 --> 00:06:52.670 line:80%
I intend

00:06:52.330 --> 00:06:58.250 line:80%
[Qi Sheng, Emperor of Great Yin]

00:06:53.430 --> 00:06:56.500 line:80%
to posthumously grant Xie Zheng
the title of the Duke of Loyal

00:06:56.500 --> 00:06:59.160 line:80%
and reward the Xie Army
with 1,000 taels of gold.

00:06:59.750 --> 00:07:02.310 line:80%
Ministers, what do you think?

00:07:07.070 --> 00:07:08.870 line:80%
Your Majesty, your wisdom shines.

00:07:08.870 --> 00:07:11.520 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an
defended the northwest

00:07:11.520 --> 00:07:12.810 line:80%
with unmatched bravery.

00:07:12.810 --> 00:07:14.930 line:80%
In the hundred-plus years
of the Great Yin dynasty,

00:07:12.950 --> 00:07:17.250 line:80%
[Li Jing, Grand Tutor of Great Yin]

00:07:15.100 --> 00:07:17.020 line:80%
only Xie Zheng

00:07:17.420 --> 00:07:19.240 line:80%
was truly worthy of such a title.

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:22.490 line:80%
Granting him the title
of Duke of Loyal posthumously now

00:07:22.490 --> 00:07:25.200 line:80%
demonstrates your virtue.

00:07:25.230 --> 00:07:27.330 line:80%
It is a blessing for the people.

00:07:27.670 --> 00:07:30.140 line:80%
In his youth,
Xie Zheng, the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:07:30.140 --> 00:07:32.880 line:80%
led troops to avenge
the humiliation at Jinzhou.

00:07:33.070 --> 00:07:36.010 line:80%
The Beijue people
tremble at the mention of his name.

00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:38.610 line:80%
All officers and soldiers
will gladly give their lives

00:07:38.530 --> 00:07:43.250 line:80%
[Diligent and Virtuous]

00:07:38.640 --> 00:07:40.600 line:80%
to repay Your Majesty's grace.

00:07:40.600 --> 00:07:41.920 line:80%
We second the motion.

00:07:42.380 --> 00:07:44.750 line:80%
Very well. Convey my decree.

00:07:45.140 --> 00:07:46.310 line:80%
In my grief,

00:07:46.330 --> 00:07:47.850 line:80%
I shall suspend court for 3 days

00:07:47.850 --> 00:07:49.140 line:80%
and wear plain robes to mourn.

00:07:49.140 --> 00:07:51.700 line:80%
The whole realm shall mourn deeply.

00:07:52.140 --> 00:07:54.530 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:07:54.900 --> 00:07:57.410 line:80%
Your Majesty, I am late.

00:08:22.570 --> 00:08:24.590 line:80%
Prime Minister, despite your ill health,

00:08:24.590 --> 00:08:25.920 line:80%
you still came to court.

00:08:26.420 --> 00:08:28.150 line:80%
This is a blessing to Great Yin.

00:08:29.090 --> 00:08:30.020 line:80%
Grant him a seat.

00:08:37.459 --> 00:08:41.120 line:80%
[Wei Yan, Prime Minister of Great Yin]

00:08:39.050 --> 00:08:40.420 line:80%
Where were we?

00:08:41.910 --> 00:08:45.300 line:80%
I intend to posthumously grant Xie Zheng
the title of the Duke of Loyal,

00:08:45.300 --> 00:08:47.240 line:80%
reward the Xie Army
with 1,000 taels of gold,

00:08:47.240 --> 00:08:48.700 line:80%
and have the nation mourn.

00:08:50.260 --> 00:08:52.390 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei, what is your view?

00:08:54.620 --> 00:08:57.170 line:80%
Though the Marquis of Wu'an
had military merit,

00:08:57.170 --> 00:08:59.900 line:80%
this matter concerns
the front-line situation.

00:09:00.490 --> 00:09:02.610 line:80%
If the entire nation mourns,

00:09:03.190 --> 00:09:06.030 line:80%
I fear it may dampen the army's morale.

00:09:06.110 --> 00:09:06.940 line:80%
At that time,

00:09:06.970 --> 00:09:09.960 line:80%
the enemy forces of Beijue
and Prince Changxin

00:09:10.420 --> 00:09:12.570 line:80%
may seize the opportunity to strike.

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:21.250 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei,

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:25.100 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an died young
in service to the state.

00:09:25.380 --> 00:09:28.380 line:80%
His Majesty's action
is out of pity for his early death

00:09:28.960 --> 00:09:31.510 line:80%
and reflects his benevolent intent.

00:09:32.410 --> 00:09:36.220 line:80%
Though scholars often criticize

00:09:36.220 --> 00:09:37.680 line:80%
his slaughter at Jinzhou,

00:09:38.060 --> 00:09:39.960 line:80%
when merits and faults are weighed,

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:42.170 line:80%
his merits far outweigh his faults.

00:09:43.060 --> 00:09:45.220 line:80%
Rewarding the Marquis of Wu'an now

00:09:45.250 --> 00:09:47.330 line:80%
is a clear act
of just reward and punishment

00:09:47.330 --> 00:09:49.350 line:80%
and a strategy that lifts morale.

00:09:49.900 --> 00:09:53.410 line:80%
Why would it weaken the army?

00:09:55.420 --> 00:09:58.050 line:80%
It has been said
that the Marquis of Wu'an fell in battle,

00:09:58.050 --> 00:10:00.410 line:80%
yet his body
hasn't been found to this day.

00:10:00.710 --> 00:10:02.500 line:80%
I have kept the news undisclosed

00:10:02.500 --> 00:10:04.670 line:80%
to mislead the enemy.

00:10:05.490 --> 00:10:08.220 line:80%
As long as his death
is not officially announced,

00:10:08.570 --> 00:10:10.930 line:80%
the enemy will not know the truth

00:10:11.660 --> 00:10:13.750 line:80%
and will not dare to advance rashly.

00:10:14.930 --> 00:10:19.160 line:80%
Grand Tutor, though you are skilled
at discerning His Majesty's intent,

00:10:19.890 --> 00:10:22.220 line:80%
you must still apply yourself diligently

00:10:22.570 --> 00:10:25.530 line:80%
to military strategy.

00:10:36.320 --> 00:10:38.610 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei, you're thoughtful.

00:10:39.730 --> 00:10:42.780 line:80%
Thank you for your guidance.

00:10:44.060 --> 00:10:45.250 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei.

00:10:51.560 --> 00:10:53.910 line:80%
My condolences.

00:10:55.030 --> 00:10:56.830 line:80%
That is kind of you, Grand Tutor.

00:10:58.380 --> 00:11:01.570 line:80%
Now that the Marquis of Wu'an
is not guarding Yanzhou,

00:11:02.560 --> 00:11:04.080 line:80%
who else

00:11:04.100 --> 00:11:06.190 line:80%
can control the Yanzhou Army?

00:11:09.390 --> 00:11:12.990 line:80%
The Yanzhou Army is also Great Yin's army.

00:11:13.170 --> 00:11:14.900 line:80%
Any capable people in the court

00:11:14.980 --> 00:11:16.950 line:80%
can go to Yanzhou.

00:11:17.720 --> 00:11:20.680 line:80%
The Yanzhou Army
concerns the safety of the border.

00:11:20.960 --> 00:11:22.710 line:80%
We must be cautious.

00:11:26.900 --> 00:11:29.170 line:80%
You have a foolproof plan.

00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:30.850 line:80%
I was worrying too much.

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:32.960 line:80%
Farewell.

00:11:43.110 --> 00:11:45.870 line:80%
This old fox cares so much about
the situation in the Northwest.

00:11:45.870 --> 00:11:49.070 line:80%
I'm afraid he wants to meddle
in border military affairs.

00:11:53.540 --> 00:11:55.580 line:80%
Has Xie Zheng's body been found?

00:11:55.730 --> 00:11:56.560 line:80%
Not yet.

00:11:58.910 --> 00:12:00.570 line:80%
Regarding the Marquis of Wu'an's
disappearance,

00:12:00.570 --> 00:12:03.190 line:80%
has the Eldest Young Master sent word?

00:12:04.020 --> 00:12:04.620 line:80%
No.

00:12:05.230 --> 00:12:08.230 line:80%
We were too close
to He Jingyuan's territory that day.

00:12:08.730 --> 00:12:10.390 line:80%
We feared alerting the enemy.

00:12:11.500 --> 00:12:14.160 line:80%
I have sent men
to continue the search in secret.

00:12:14.220 --> 00:12:15.200 line:80%
Keep searching.

00:12:15.590 --> 00:12:16.620 line:80%
Tell him to hurry.

00:12:16.650 --> 00:12:17.170 line:80%
Yes.

00:12:17.650 --> 00:12:20.650 line:80%
We must confirm he's dead or alive.

00:12:20.690 --> 00:12:23.340 line:80%
But the key is finding that token.

00:12:23.340 --> 00:12:23.770 line:80%
Yes.

00:12:23.900 --> 00:12:25.760 line:80%
Tell the people of the Black Cross

00:12:26.430 --> 00:12:27.390 line:80%
not to come back

00:12:28.410 --> 00:12:29.600 line:80%
if they can't find it.

00:12:29.600 --> 00:12:30.480 line:80%
Yes.

00:13:55.610 --> 00:14:00.850 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:14:00.940 --> 00:14:03.670 line:80%
[Episode 3]

00:14:04.840 --> 00:14:05.530 line:80%
Go away!

00:14:07.050 --> 00:14:07.890 line:80%
Get lost!

00:14:08.660 --> 00:14:09.450 line:80%
Go away!

00:14:10.570 --> 00:14:11.490 line:80%
Go away!

00:14:11.510 --> 00:14:12.220 line:80%
Go away!

00:14:12.410 --> 00:14:13.270 line:80%
Go away!

00:14:16.050 --> 00:14:16.770 line:80%
Go away!

00:14:16.800 --> 00:14:17.520 line:80%
Go away!

00:14:18.900 --> 00:14:19.780 line:80%
Go away!

00:14:23.670 --> 00:14:25.470 line:80%
Where did that wild wolf come from?

00:14:25.470 --> 00:14:27.130 line:80%
It nearly took my hair ribbon.

00:14:31.570 --> 00:14:32.500 line:80%
Where is my shoe?

00:15:02.690 --> 00:15:05.220 line:80%
This young lady
really doesn't fear the cold.

00:15:05.410 --> 00:15:06.700 line:80%
It's snowing heavily,

00:15:06.720 --> 00:15:08.390 line:80%
yet she's walking barefoot.

00:15:22.220 --> 00:15:24.310 line:80%
She must have met with some trouble
on the road.

00:15:24.310 --> 00:15:25.520 line:80%
Ask where she lives.

00:15:25.550 --> 00:15:26.750 line:80%
We'll give her a ride.

00:15:28.060 --> 00:15:28.910 line:80%
Miss.

00:15:31.980 --> 00:15:34.220 line:80%
My master can't bear to see you
struggling in the snow

00:15:34.220 --> 00:15:35.350 line:80%
and offers you a ride.

00:15:35.350 --> 00:15:36.350 line:80%
Where do you live?

00:15:37.740 --> 00:15:39.260 line:80%
No need. Thank you.

00:15:42.590 --> 00:15:43.650 line:80%
Miss, please wait.

00:15:56.020 --> 00:15:56.880 line:80%
My surname is Li.

00:15:56.880 --> 00:15:58.010 line:80%
I'm not a bad person.

00:15:58.540 --> 00:15:59.770 line:80%
Walking barefoot in this weather,

00:15:59.770 --> 00:16:01.120 line:80%
your feet will be ruined.

00:16:01.120 --> 00:16:02.320 line:80%
Let me give you a ride.

00:16:07.260 --> 00:16:08.620 line:80%
Well, thank you, sir.

00:16:18.050 --> 00:16:19.260 line:80%
Thank you, sir.

00:16:33.900 --> 00:16:35.560 line:80%
But with you sitting outside,

00:16:35.700 --> 00:16:37.150 line:80%
I feel bad.

00:16:37.800 --> 00:16:38.520 line:80%
It's fine.

00:16:38.690 --> 00:16:39.820 line:80%
Miss, your shoes and socks are soaked.

00:16:39.820 --> 00:16:40.630 line:80%
Dry them off.

00:16:41.280 --> 00:16:42.860 line:80%
I was getting stuffy in the carriage.

00:16:42.860 --> 00:16:44.120 line:80%
I came out for some air.

00:16:56.850 --> 00:16:59.250 line:80%
Changyu, you're back so early.

00:16:59.740 --> 00:17:00.740 line:80%
Changyu.

00:17:01.270 --> 00:17:03.100 line:80%
What... what happened to you?

00:17:04.649 --> 00:17:06.139 line:80%
I met a wild wolf on the way

00:17:06.360 --> 00:17:07.960 line:80%
and lost a shoe running away.

00:17:08.100 --> 00:17:10.360 line:80%
Thanks to these two gentlemen
for bringing me back.

00:17:10.360 --> 00:17:11.220 line:80%
It was nothing.

00:17:12.129 --> 00:17:13.700 line:80%
Thank you, gentlemen.

00:17:14.340 --> 00:17:15.580 line:80%
It's freezing.

00:17:15.580 --> 00:17:16.820 line:80%
Come in and warm up.

00:17:16.820 --> 00:17:17.409 line:80%
Ma'am,

00:17:17.740 --> 00:17:19.740 line:80%
let Miss Fan change her shoes first.

00:17:19.740 --> 00:17:21.010 line:80%
We have urgent matters.

00:17:21.010 --> 00:17:22.210 line:80%
We'll take our leave.

00:17:22.610 --> 00:17:23.810 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Li.

00:17:26.690 --> 00:17:28.090 line:80%
Sorry for the intrusion.

00:17:28.280 --> 00:17:29.280 line:80%
Please wait.

00:17:29.450 --> 00:17:31.470 line:80%
Here are some freshly roasted chestnuts.

00:17:31.470 --> 00:17:33.080 line:80%
Take them for the road.

00:17:33.100 --> 00:17:33.670 line:80%
No need.

00:17:33.690 --> 00:17:36.280 line:80%
My auntie roasts delicious chestnuts.

00:17:36.300 --> 00:17:37.630 line:80%
Yes, they taste great.

00:17:37.780 --> 00:17:38.970 line:80%
Please try some.

00:17:39.000 --> 00:17:40.230 line:80%
It would be impolite to refuse.

00:17:40.230 --> 00:17:41.230 line:80%
Thank you, ma'am.

00:17:41.580 --> 00:17:43.310 line:80%
-Okay. Wait a minute.
-M'am...

00:17:45.610 --> 00:17:46.680 line:80%
Why did you say yes?

00:17:46.760 --> 00:17:48.370 line:80%
The villagers' way of showing gratitude

00:17:48.370 --> 00:17:49.410 line:80%
is just this simple.

00:17:49.410 --> 00:17:51.260 line:80%
We need to blend in with them.

00:17:51.800 --> 00:17:53.730 line:80%
It helps with your investigation.

00:17:53.730 --> 00:17:54.340 line:80%
Right?

00:17:55.430 --> 00:17:57.520 line:80%
Just admit you're craving them.

00:18:15.780 --> 00:18:17.190 line:80%
I didn't see anything.

00:18:21.670 --> 00:18:22.320 line:80%
Come in.

00:18:29.100 --> 00:18:29.930 line:80%
I... I...

00:18:30.010 --> 00:18:33.970 line:80%
I went to Mrs. Chen's
to tailor the wedding clothes today

00:18:33.970 --> 00:18:36.030 line:80%
and realized I forgot to measure you.

00:18:38.350 --> 00:18:39.110 line:80%
Come on in.

00:19:05.140 --> 00:19:06.990 line:80%
You look thin,

00:19:07.930 --> 00:19:09.930 line:80%
but your shoulders are quite broad.

00:19:10.660 --> 00:19:11.790 line:80%
Just like my father.

00:19:12.460 --> 00:19:13.900 line:80%
Shoulder width, 1.8 chi.

00:19:27.860 --> 00:19:29.210 line:80%
Waist, 2.1 chi.

00:19:31.850 --> 00:19:33.610 line:80%
Legs, 3.7 chi.

00:19:37.040 --> 00:19:37.840 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:19:38.860 --> 00:19:39.780 line:80%
Nothing.

00:19:40.010 --> 00:19:41.590 line:80%
I was chased by a wolf this morning.

00:19:41.590 --> 00:19:43.320 line:80%
I might have sprained my ankle.

00:19:43.970 --> 00:19:45.320 line:80%
Sit down. Let me check.

00:19:45.350 --> 00:19:46.110 line:80%
No need.

00:19:47.020 --> 00:19:48.860 line:80%
Mr. Zhao will be back soon.

00:19:49.010 --> 00:19:50.740 line:80%
I'll just apply some medicine.

00:19:56.410 --> 00:19:57.450 line:80%
Sit down.

00:19:57.670 --> 00:19:58.560 line:80%
Let me take a look.

00:19:58.560 --> 00:20:00.220 line:80%
Or it will hurt again tonight.

00:20:02.930 --> 00:20:03.730 line:80%
Is it good?

00:20:03.730 --> 00:20:04.730 line:80%
Yes.

00:20:12.470 --> 00:20:13.400 line:80%
I don't know why,

00:20:14.140 --> 00:20:17.200 line:80%
but those mysterious people retreated
at Lin'an Town.

00:20:22.100 --> 00:20:23.850 line:80%
They vanished completely.

00:20:24.700 --> 00:20:25.550 line:80%
Should I

00:20:25.740 --> 00:20:28.010 line:80%
ask the local magistrate of Lin'an?

00:20:29.880 --> 00:20:31.080 line:80%
My mentor said

00:20:31.340 --> 00:20:33.140 line:80%
this matter must be kept secret.

00:20:39.490 --> 00:20:40.120 line:80%
My Lord,

00:20:40.440 --> 00:20:41.780 line:80%
you've been searching
for the Marquis of Wu'an

00:20:41.780 --> 00:20:43.060 line:80%
night after night,

00:20:43.290 --> 00:20:44.690 line:80%
but we still have no news.

00:20:45.140 --> 00:20:46.110 line:80%
If you ask me,

00:20:46.540 --> 00:20:47.800 line:80%
in the chaos of war,

00:20:47.820 --> 00:20:49.480 line:80%
disappearing without a trace

00:20:49.650 --> 00:20:50.780 line:80%
is nothing new.

00:20:51.170 --> 00:20:52.170 line:80%
I feel like

00:20:53.580 --> 00:20:56.040 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an
wouldn't die so easily.

00:20:58.250 --> 00:21:00.650 line:80%
If those mysterious people are lingering,

00:21:01.560 --> 00:21:03.960 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an
must be in Lin'an Town.

00:21:09.860 --> 00:21:10.860 line:80%
It's dislocated.

00:21:12.620 --> 00:21:13.420 line:80%
It hurts!

00:21:13.450 --> 00:21:15.110 line:80%
Of course a dislocation hurts.

00:21:15.110 --> 00:21:17.290 line:80%
I thought it was just a sprain.

00:21:18.420 --> 00:21:19.290 line:80%
Bear with it.

00:21:23.970 --> 00:21:24.830 line:80%
Done.

00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:35.530 line:80%
My Lords,

00:21:36.080 --> 00:21:37.610 line:80%
freshly roasted chestnuts.

00:21:37.610 --> 00:21:38.650 line:80%
They are still warm.

00:21:38.650 --> 00:21:39.650 line:80%
Eat them while they're hot.

00:21:39.650 --> 00:21:40.490 line:80%
Thank you, ma'am.

00:21:40.490 --> 00:21:41.010 line:80%
Ma'am,

00:21:41.990 --> 00:21:42.850 line:80%
I just heard

00:21:42.870 --> 00:21:44.630 line:80%
Miss Fan screaming in the attic.

00:21:44.630 --> 00:21:45.760 line:80%
Is something wrong?

00:21:46.310 --> 00:21:48.550 line:80%
That is Changyu's husband.

00:21:48.960 --> 00:21:51.060 line:80%
The young couple
is probably just playing around.

00:21:51.060 --> 00:21:51.910 line:80%
Husband?

00:21:54.010 --> 00:21:56.830 line:80%
Why didn't he come down
to welcome Miss Fan just now?

00:21:56.830 --> 00:21:57.990 line:80%
He has an injury.

00:21:58.020 --> 00:21:59.480 line:80%
He can't come down easily.

00:22:01.360 --> 00:22:02.010 line:80%
Is it good?

00:22:02.030 --> 00:22:03.440 line:80%
It's delicious, ma'am.

00:22:03.950 --> 00:22:05.810 line:80%
The Northwest is at war right now.

00:22:06.020 --> 00:22:07.300 line:80%
I heard many injured refugees
from Chongzhou

00:22:07.300 --> 00:22:09.120 line:80%
came here,

00:22:09.150 --> 00:22:10.950 line:80%
hoping to marry and settle down.

00:22:11.060 --> 00:22:12.400 line:80%
Is Miss Fan's husband

00:22:12.970 --> 00:22:14.430 line:80%
from Chongzhou too?

00:22:18.620 --> 00:22:20.630 line:80%
He is a distant relative of mine

00:22:20.650 --> 00:22:21.900 line:80%
from Yanzhou.

00:22:22.800 --> 00:22:23.760 line:80%
Yanzhou?

00:22:29.190 --> 00:22:30.760 line:80%
It's really healed.

00:22:31.340 --> 00:22:32.600 line:80%
It doesn't hurt at all.

00:22:37.140 --> 00:22:38.540 line:80%
I told you not to wolf it down.

00:22:38.540 --> 00:22:39.820 line:80%
You choked, didn't you?

00:22:39.820 --> 00:22:40.380 line:80%
Ma'am,

00:22:40.710 --> 00:22:42.010 line:80%
may we have some tea?

00:22:42.040 --> 00:22:43.030 line:80%
Sure.

00:22:43.710 --> 00:22:45.200 line:80%
I was so focused on the food

00:22:45.220 --> 00:22:46.240 line:80%
and forgot the drinks.

00:22:46.240 --> 00:22:46.760 line:80%
Come.

00:22:46.830 --> 00:22:47.780 line:80%
Come in and have some tea.

00:22:47.780 --> 00:22:48.380 line:80%
Thank you.

00:22:55.860 --> 00:22:57.190 line:80%
Is someone downstairs?

00:22:57.910 --> 00:22:58.560 line:80%
Oh no.

00:22:59.010 --> 00:23:01.010 line:80%
I forgot my two saviors downstairs.

00:23:05.970 --> 00:23:08.080 line:80%
Please excuse the poor tea.

00:23:08.890 --> 00:23:11.020 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, did you just get married?

00:23:14.090 --> 00:23:15.020 line:80%
Actually,

00:23:15.860 --> 00:23:17.340 line:80%
he married into my family.

00:23:18.450 --> 00:23:20.050 line:80%
He married into your family?

00:23:20.460 --> 00:23:22.460 line:80%
He's a poor child.

00:23:22.490 --> 00:23:24.970 line:80%
He just came to Lin'an from Yanzhou

00:23:25.140 --> 00:23:26.200 line:80%
and ran into bandits

00:23:26.200 --> 00:23:27.050 line:80%
who robbed

00:23:27.070 --> 00:23:28.140 line:80%
and injured him.

00:23:28.750 --> 00:23:31.170 line:80%
Luckily, our Zhangyu took him in.

00:23:31.200 --> 00:23:32.490 line:80%
She even butchered a pig

00:23:32.490 --> 00:23:34.490 line:80%
and sold it to pay for his treatment.

00:23:35.110 --> 00:23:36.090 line:80%
Butchered a pig?

00:23:38.230 --> 00:23:40.140 line:80%
My sister is amazing.

00:23:40.850 --> 00:23:43.040 line:80%
She can knock out a pig with one slap.

00:23:43.870 --> 00:23:45.450 line:80%
She's kidding.

00:23:50.580 --> 00:23:52.080 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, you're truly virtuous.

00:23:52.080 --> 00:23:53.250 line:80%
Truly virtuous.

00:23:58.080 --> 00:23:59.740 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, no need to see us off.

00:24:00.210 --> 00:24:00.800 line:80%
Here.

00:24:02.580 --> 00:24:03.490 line:80%
Take care.

00:24:08.060 --> 00:24:08.690 line:80%
My Lord.

00:24:09.500 --> 00:24:11.120 line:80%
I think we have lost our minds
trying to find

00:24:11.120 --> 00:24:12.380 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:24:12.560 --> 00:24:14.100 line:80%
He's the kind of man who even refused

00:24:14.100 --> 00:24:15.170 line:80%
a princess.

00:24:15.350 --> 00:24:17.540 line:80%
How could he possibly
marry a butcher girl,

00:24:17.540 --> 00:24:20.200 line:80%
giving her foot massages
and setting her bones?

00:24:20.370 --> 00:24:21.730 line:80%
I overthought it.

00:24:21.980 --> 00:24:24.230 line:80%
You haven't slept in days because of this.

00:24:24.230 --> 00:24:26.440 line:80%
Have a good sleep
on the way back to Jizhou.

00:24:26.440 --> 00:24:28.040 line:80%
I'll handle things outside.

00:24:28.840 --> 00:24:29.460 line:80%
Let's go.

00:24:44.360 --> 00:24:45.920 line:80%
A carriage from Jizhou?

00:24:46.490 --> 00:24:48.020 line:80%
They're He Jingyuan's men.

00:24:54.390 --> 00:24:56.790 line:80%
What were Yan Zheng's measurements again?

00:25:06.540 --> 00:25:07.900 line:80%
Shoulder width...

00:25:11.000 --> 00:25:12.440 line:80%
1.8 chi.

00:25:13.430 --> 00:25:16.570 line:80%
Waist... 2.1 chi.

00:25:14.860 --> 00:25:17.110 line:80%
[1.8 chi] [2.1 chi]

00:25:18.790 --> 00:25:20.020 line:80%
Legs...

00:25:19.830 --> 00:25:22.550 line:80%
[1.8 chi] [2.1 chi] [3.7 chi]

00:25:20.980 --> 00:25:22.110 line:80%
3.7 chi.

00:25:33.100 --> 00:25:34.730 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:25:36.510 --> 00:25:37.650 line:80%
Yan Zheng?

00:25:43.530 --> 00:25:46.010 line:80%
[Xie]

00:25:49.890 --> 00:25:52.180 line:80%
[Xie Zheng]

00:25:54.820 --> 00:26:00.800 line:80%
[Xie Zheng]

00:26:04.030 --> 00:26:05.180 line:80%
This is...

00:26:06.140 --> 00:26:07.730 line:80%
Did she discover something?

00:26:06.970 --> 00:26:08.950 line:80%
[Xie Zheng]

00:26:19.900 --> 00:26:20.540 line:80%
Who is it?

00:26:21.650 --> 00:26:22.450 line:80%
It's me.

00:26:23.160 --> 00:26:24.760 line:80%
I have something to tell you.

00:26:28.410 --> 00:26:29.060 line:80%
Come in.

00:26:44.700 --> 00:26:46.620 line:80%
I've noted the measurements.

00:26:47.400 --> 00:26:48.930 line:80%
I'll send them over in a bit.

00:27:00.850 --> 00:27:03.230 line:80%
Can you stay up tonight?

00:27:03.670 --> 00:27:05.600 line:80%
Wait for me. I have something to do.

00:27:08.740 --> 00:27:11.320 line:80%
It can only be done if we do it together.

00:27:17.740 --> 00:27:19.100 line:80%
Together?

00:27:19.400 --> 00:27:21.000 line:80%
You're a man, and I'm a woman.

00:27:21.260 --> 00:27:22.930 line:80%
I can't do it without you.

00:27:34.500 --> 00:27:36.430 line:80%
That wouldn't be proper, would it?

00:27:36.940 --> 00:27:38.170 line:80%
You'll be my matrilocal husband soon.

00:27:38.170 --> 00:27:39.630 line:80%
What's improper about it?

00:27:39.900 --> 00:27:40.960 line:80%
It's settled then.

00:27:51.350 --> 00:27:53.680 line:80%
Don't let Mr. Zhao and Mrs. Zhao
know about this.

00:27:53.680 --> 00:27:54.610 line:80%
Keep it a secret.

00:28:36.860 --> 00:28:38.260 line:80%
What do you want me to do?

00:28:38.380 --> 00:28:40.380 line:80%
Don't let anyone see you. Follow me.

00:28:49.810 --> 00:28:50.660 line:80%
Kneel.

00:28:59.320 --> 00:29:01.130 line:80%
This is the thing

00:29:01.830 --> 00:29:03.490 line:80%
you said we had to do together?

00:29:05.930 --> 00:29:06.990 line:80%
My mother said that

00:29:07.240 --> 00:29:09.970 line:80%
when visiting a grave at midnight,
you need a man,

00:29:10.730 --> 00:29:12.390 line:80%
a man with strong yang energy.

00:29:12.660 --> 00:29:13.560 line:80%
That's you.

00:29:13.900 --> 00:29:16.630 line:80%
[Xie Zheng, Marquis of Wu'an]

00:29:19.360 --> 00:29:21.550 line:80%
[Xie Zheng, Marquis of Wu'an]

00:29:21.570 --> 00:29:24.590 line:80%
[Xie Zheng]

00:29:28.410 --> 00:29:29.730 line:80%
So that's why she was writing that

00:29:29.730 --> 00:29:31.820 line:80%
in the sand earlier today.

00:29:33.740 --> 00:29:35.690 line:80%
The authorities
haven't issued an obituary.

00:29:35.690 --> 00:29:38.730 line:80%
I was afraid that private mourning
could get us in trouble.

00:29:38.730 --> 00:29:41.250 line:80%
It's best to do it at midnight
when no one's around.

00:29:41.250 --> 00:29:42.710 line:80%
And this memorial tablet?

00:29:45.940 --> 00:29:47.890 line:80%
You were coughing up blood badly
back then.

00:29:47.890 --> 00:29:49.620 line:80%
I thought you wouldn't make it,

00:29:50.340 --> 00:29:51.740 line:80%
so I had it carved for you.

00:29:53.720 --> 00:29:54.710 line:80%
Thank you.

00:29:55.120 --> 00:29:57.450 line:80%
Don't mention it. We didn't use it anyway.

00:30:00.020 --> 00:30:02.220 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an has died in battle.

00:30:02.610 --> 00:30:04.930 line:80%
I wanted to set up a memorial tablet
for him.

00:30:04.930 --> 00:30:05.900 line:80%
Surprisingly,

00:30:06.170 --> 00:30:08.700 line:80%
a small change to your name
could make it work.

00:30:09.540 --> 00:30:10.300 line:80%
Yeah.

00:30:11.040 --> 00:30:12.700 line:80%
It works out perfectly for me.

00:30:13.970 --> 00:30:15.080 line:80%
It's yellow rosewood.

00:30:15.080 --> 00:30:16.610 line:80%
It'd be a waste not to use it.

00:30:17.900 --> 00:30:18.570 line:80%
By the way,

00:30:18.600 --> 00:30:20.930 line:80%
you came here as a refugee from Chongzhou.

00:30:21.130 --> 00:30:23.390 line:80%
Do you know how the Marquis of Wu'an died?

00:30:24.350 --> 00:30:24.960 line:80%
I don't.

00:30:28.840 --> 00:30:31.240 line:80%
You're not related
to the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:30:31.700 --> 00:30:33.700 line:80%
Why set up a memorial tablet for him?

00:30:34.060 --> 00:30:35.500 line:80%
Doesn't everyone say

00:30:36.020 --> 00:30:38.380 line:80%
that the Marquis of Wu'an
is a bloodthirsty,

00:30:38.380 --> 00:30:40.490 line:80%
violent living Yama
who slaughtered a city?

00:30:40.490 --> 00:30:41.340 line:80%
Nonsense!

00:30:42.690 --> 00:30:43.620 line:80%
My father said

00:30:44.320 --> 00:30:45.560 line:80%
he led the army

00:30:46.020 --> 00:30:47.980 line:80%
and took back Jinzhou from Beijue,

00:30:48.580 --> 00:30:49.710 line:80%
avenging his father

00:30:50.930 --> 00:30:52.250 line:80%
and Great Yin.

00:30:53.340 --> 00:30:54.540 line:80%
As for the slaughter—

00:30:55.580 --> 00:30:56.910 line:80%
if the enemy could do it,

00:30:57.930 --> 00:30:59.170 line:80%
why couldn't he?

00:31:07.900 --> 00:31:09.160 line:80%
Do you really think so?

00:31:10.820 --> 00:31:12.720 line:80%
My father often told me

00:31:12.840 --> 00:31:14.770 line:80%
that in over 200 years of Great Yin,

00:31:14.840 --> 00:31:17.100 line:80%
there has been only one Marquis of Wu'an.

00:31:17.520 --> 00:31:19.180 line:80%
Jinzhou was reclaimed by him.

00:31:21.060 --> 00:31:22.860 line:80%
The 12 prefectures of Liaodong,

00:31:23.250 --> 00:31:25.100 line:80%
which had suffered the loss
of countless loyal ministers

00:31:25.100 --> 00:31:26.780 line:80%
and distinguished generals
in decades of war,

00:31:26.780 --> 00:31:28.310 line:80%
were also taken back by him.

00:31:29.360 --> 00:31:31.080 line:80%
The scholars of our time

00:31:32.900 --> 00:31:34.330 line:80%
all despise what he did.

00:31:35.410 --> 00:31:36.650 line:80%
Those scholars

00:31:37.140 --> 00:31:39.000 line:80%
say he is cold-blooded and cruel.

00:31:39.430 --> 00:31:41.400 line:80%
But what about the soldiers and civilians

00:31:41.400 --> 00:31:43.770 line:80%
who died in Jinzhou 16 years ago?

00:31:43.990 --> 00:31:45.460 line:80%
Were they not innocent?

00:31:45.970 --> 00:31:47.640 line:80%
Old General Xie died standing tall

00:31:47.640 --> 00:31:49.030 line:80%
to maintain his dignity,

00:31:49.030 --> 00:31:51.030 line:80%
but the Beijue people disemboweled him

00:31:51.030 --> 00:31:52.410 line:80%
and displayed his body on the city wall.

00:31:52.410 --> 00:31:54.470 line:80%
He was the Marquis of Wu'an's father.

00:31:57.710 --> 00:32:00.290 line:80%
It is only right to avenge one's father.

00:32:00.640 --> 00:32:02.260 line:80%
Without the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:32:02.260 --> 00:32:03.630 line:80%
who else

00:32:04.010 --> 00:32:05.700 line:80%
could hold the northwest?

00:32:10.560 --> 00:32:12.470 line:80%
Why are you looking at me like that?

00:32:12.470 --> 00:32:13.570 line:80%
Am I wrong?

00:32:16.170 --> 00:32:17.970 line:80%
You really dare to say anything.

00:32:20.030 --> 00:32:29.930 line:80%
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

00:32:21.680 --> 00:32:23.080 line:80%
There's no one else here.

00:32:23.320 --> 00:32:24.850 line:80%
That's why I dared to say it.

00:32:30.740 --> 00:32:40.330 line:80%
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

00:32:36.130 --> 00:32:37.370 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an,

00:32:38.040 --> 00:32:39.560 line:80%
I, Fan Changyu,

00:32:40.110 --> 00:32:41.370 line:80%
together with my husband, Yan Zheng,

00:32:41.370 --> 00:32:42.640 line:80%
have come to see you off.

00:32:41.370 --> 00:32:46.070 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:32:46.090 --> 00:32:50.990 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:32:46.230 --> 00:32:47.940 line:80%
May your spirit in heaven

00:32:48.380 --> 00:32:51.240 line:80%
bless the people of Great Yin
with peace and safety.

00:32:51.630 --> 00:32:53.750 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:32:52.740 --> 00:32:54.400 line:80%
If you happen to meet my parents,

00:32:54.340 --> 00:32:57.050 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:32:57.670 --> 00:33:03.610 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:32:57.950 --> 00:32:59.690 line:80%
please send them my regards.

00:33:10.270 --> 00:33:11.700 line:80%
If you have any wishes,

00:33:12.130 --> 00:33:13.990 line:80%
kneel down, kowtow, and tell him.

00:33:16.200 --> 00:33:18.300 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an died for our country.

00:33:18.300 --> 00:33:20.500 line:80%
You'll lose nothing by kneeling to him.

00:33:21.870 --> 00:33:26.450 line:80%
♪ In the east wind,
flowers bloom at night ♪

00:33:27.480 --> 00:33:30.480 line:80%
♪ Blowing down the stars like rain ♪

00:33:32.860 --> 00:33:35.130 line:80%
♪ Fine horses and carved carriages
fill the fragrant streets ♪

00:33:35.510 --> 00:33:37.420 line:80%
♪ The phoenix flute resounds ♪

00:33:38.030 --> 00:33:39.290 line:80%
♪ The jade pot light revolves ♪

00:33:39.580 --> 00:33:43.230 line:80%
♪ A night of fish-and-dragon dances ♪

00:33:41.720 --> 00:33:46.560 line:80%
[Xie Zheng, Marquis of Wu'an]

00:33:43.500 --> 00:33:48.100 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:33:43.980 --> 00:33:46.150 line:80%
May the fog clear soon.

00:33:47.690 --> 00:33:49.130 line:80%
May the truth

00:33:48.120 --> 00:33:53.120 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:33:50.380 --> 00:33:52.180 line:80%
be revealed to all.

00:33:53.680 --> 00:33:55.810 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:33:56.420 --> 00:34:00.910 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:34:02.510 --> 00:34:12.019 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:34:18.630 --> 00:34:24.979 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:34:35.019 --> 00:34:36.900 line:80%
Changyu.

00:34:37.990 --> 00:34:39.390 line:80%
Changyu.

00:34:40.510 --> 00:34:42.680 line:80%
My braid is crooked.

00:34:42.700 --> 00:34:44.060 line:80%
Come here and let me see.

00:34:45.269 --> 00:34:46.590 line:80%
I'm here.

00:34:51.150 --> 00:34:51.749 line:80%
Come.

00:34:55.300 --> 00:34:56.450 line:80%
It's not crooked.

00:34:58.970 --> 00:35:00.450 line:80%
Just make do with it for today.

00:35:00.450 --> 00:35:01.570 line:80%
When I finish selling the pork,

00:35:01.570 --> 00:35:03.230 line:80%
I'll buy you some candy, okay?

00:35:03.990 --> 00:35:04.850 line:80%
Go get dressed.

00:35:06.330 --> 00:35:07.360 line:80%
Be careful.

00:35:16.580 --> 00:35:17.450 line:80%
Morning, Changyu.

00:35:17.450 --> 00:35:18.180 line:80%
Morning.

00:35:18.210 --> 00:35:19.320 line:80%
Going to work, Changyu?

00:35:19.320 --> 00:35:20.650 line:80%
Morning, ma'am.

00:35:22.180 --> 00:35:23.170 line:80%
Morning, Changyu.

00:35:23.170 --> 00:35:23.860 line:80%
Morning.

00:35:24.050 --> 00:35:24.700 line:80%
Morning.

00:35:24.730 --> 00:35:25.320 line:80%
Morning.

00:35:25.750 --> 00:35:26.240 line:80%
Changyu.

00:35:26.240 --> 00:35:26.790 line:80%
Morning.

00:35:26.820 --> 00:35:27.780 line:80%
Morning, Changyu.

00:35:27.780 --> 00:35:28.670 line:80%
Morning.

00:35:40.150 --> 00:35:43.840 line:80%
[Meat]

00:35:42.740 --> 00:35:43.790 line:80%
Changyu,

00:35:44.170 --> 00:35:46.900 line:80%
are you giving away
the braised pig hearts today?

00:35:47.030 --> 00:35:48.130 line:80%
Not today.

00:35:48.150 --> 00:35:50.080 line:80%
These braised pig hearts are for sale.

00:35:50.080 --> 00:35:52.070 line:80%
I only gave them away on opening day.

00:35:52.070 --> 00:35:53.820 line:80%
I won't be giving them away anymore.

00:35:53.820 --> 00:35:55.130 line:80%
If you want some,

00:35:55.160 --> 00:35:56.680 line:80%
it's 30 mace a jin.

00:35:57.880 --> 00:36:01.340 line:80%
Others give braised offal for free
when you buy meat.

00:36:01.360 --> 00:36:03.180 line:80%
Why do you charge for it?

00:36:03.340 --> 00:36:04.380 line:80%
Which place?

00:36:05.460 --> 00:36:06.720 line:80%
Butcher Guo

00:36:06.830 --> 00:36:08.680 line:80%
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

00:36:06.880 --> 00:36:08.770 line:80%
gives away braised offal
with meat purchases.

00:36:08.770 --> 00:36:10.770 line:80%
Buy meat and get free braised offal!

00:36:13.580 --> 00:36:14.350 line:80%
Come!

00:36:14.380 --> 00:36:16.380 line:80%
Buy meat and get free braised offal!

00:36:17.130 --> 00:36:18.410 line:80%
Are you giving it away or not?

00:36:18.410 --> 00:36:20.630 line:80%
If not, I'm going to his shop.

00:36:22.570 --> 00:36:24.080 line:80%
Yes, of course I am.

00:36:23.900 --> 00:36:27.810 line:80%
[Meat]

00:36:24.700 --> 00:36:26.120 line:80%
Then I won't go to his place.

00:36:26.120 --> 00:36:27.850 line:80%
I'd like 2 jin of pork shoulder.

00:36:30.650 --> 00:36:32.180 line:80%
Mrs. Tao, here's your meat.

00:36:33.300 --> 00:36:35.180 line:80%
Here is your braised pig heart. Take it.

00:36:35.180 --> 00:36:35.820 line:80%
Great.

00:36:35.930 --> 00:36:39.180 line:80%
[Meat]

00:36:40.970 --> 00:36:42.050 line:80%
Here, young lady.

00:36:42.450 --> 00:36:43.280 line:80%
Here's your meat.

00:36:43.280 --> 00:36:43.780 line:80%
Okay.

00:36:44.080 --> 00:36:45.870 line:80%
That Guo is full of tricks.

00:36:46.040 --> 00:36:47.490 line:80%
He wouldn't let you give extras,

00:36:47.490 --> 00:36:49.290 line:80%
but he started doing it himself.

00:36:50.130 --> 00:36:52.400 line:80%
He has an uncle who is an advisor
at the county government office.

00:36:52.400 --> 00:36:53.630 line:80%
Be careful.

00:36:54.710 --> 00:36:55.380 line:80%
Got it.

00:36:55.630 --> 00:36:56.620 line:80%
Look how good this meat is.

00:36:56.620 --> 00:36:57.850 line:80%
Let's go to Fan's.

00:36:57.870 --> 00:36:59.150 line:80%
The lean meat is redder there,

00:36:59.150 --> 00:37:00.210 line:80%
and the braised food smells good.

00:37:00.210 --> 00:37:01.750 line:80%
Unlike the pork here.
It doesn't smell fresh.

00:37:01.750 --> 00:37:06.340 line:80%
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

00:37:01.880 --> 00:37:04.110 line:80%
Hey, what do you mean by that?

00:37:04.500 --> 00:37:06.700 line:80%
Is their brine made of liquid gold?

00:37:07.550 --> 00:37:09.190 line:80%
Good thing you're back.

00:37:10.850 --> 00:37:13.680 line:80%
Let's see how long he can keep giving

00:37:13.970 --> 00:37:15.970 line:80%
the offal boiled in salt water away.

00:37:16.710 --> 00:37:18.320 line:80%
Talking about me, huh?

00:37:18.410 --> 00:37:18.900 line:80%
Fine.

00:37:19.850 --> 00:37:22.380 line:80%
Just you wait.

00:37:23.410 --> 00:37:25.670 line:80%
Mrs. Yin, where are my noodles?

00:37:25.700 --> 00:37:26.740 line:80%
What's the rush?

00:37:26.760 --> 00:37:27.790 line:80%
Like a starving ghost.

00:37:27.790 --> 00:37:28.500 line:80%
I'm coming.

00:37:28.520 --> 00:37:29.600 line:80%
I am hungry.

00:37:30.660 --> 00:37:31.470 line:80%
Hurry up.

00:37:32.240 --> 00:37:32.910 line:80%
Changyu,

00:37:32.930 --> 00:37:34.080 line:80%
I'm going back first.

00:37:34.080 --> 00:37:35.820 line:80%
If that Guo dares to bully you again,

00:37:35.820 --> 00:37:36.740 line:80%
just tell me.

00:37:36.890 --> 00:37:37.920 line:80%
I'm not afraid of him.

00:37:37.920 --> 00:37:39.520 line:80%
I'm not afraid of him either.

00:37:40.220 --> 00:37:40.930 line:80%
I'm off.

00:37:41.730 --> 00:37:46.030 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:37:41.860 --> 00:37:43.080 line:80%
How many jin of meat do you want?

00:37:43.080 --> 00:37:43.940 line:80%
Two would be fine.

00:37:43.940 --> 00:37:45.270 line:80%
-Two jin, right?
-Two jin for me, too.

00:37:45.270 --> 00:37:45.870 line:80%
Okay.

00:38:22.410 --> 00:38:23.180 line:80%
Stupid bird.

00:38:23.400 --> 00:38:25.130 line:80%
Falling for such a crude trap.

00:38:35.300 --> 00:38:35.930 line:80%
Come up.

00:38:47.700 --> 00:38:48.340 line:80%
Go on.

00:38:55.790 --> 00:38:58.790 line:80%
[Wuqi has arrived at
Four Seasons Bookshop in Lin'an]

00:39:06.640 --> 00:39:07.230 line:80%
Hurry up.

00:39:08.340 --> 00:39:09.280 line:80%
Listen to me.

00:39:09.300 --> 00:39:10.430 line:80%
While that girl is away,

00:39:10.430 --> 00:39:11.610 line:80%
search the place thoroughly.

00:39:11.610 --> 00:39:12.790 line:80%
You go check outside the yard first.

00:39:12.790 --> 00:39:13.740 line:80%
See if anyone else is there.

00:39:13.740 --> 00:39:15.740 line:80%
-Okay.
-I'll go to the second floor.

00:39:20.130 --> 00:39:21.390 line:80%
No one in the backyard.

00:39:27.280 --> 00:39:28.880 line:80%
No one in the kitchen either.

00:39:33.340 --> 00:39:34.790 line:80%
No one upstairs either.

00:39:44.060 --> 00:39:46.110 line:80%
I shouldn't cause trouble now.

00:39:46.340 --> 00:39:48.680 line:80%
They can't find anything valuable anyway.

00:39:48.680 --> 00:39:49.840 line:80%
Let me tell you,

00:39:49.920 --> 00:39:51.620 line:80%
if we don't find the title deed this time,

00:39:51.620 --> 00:39:53.140 line:80%
we'll lose our jobs.

00:39:53.160 --> 00:39:54.220 line:80%
Look carefully!

00:39:54.710 --> 00:39:55.420 line:80%
Okay.

00:40:07.870 --> 00:40:09.720 line:80%
Mr. Wang, you look quite busy today.

00:40:09.720 --> 00:40:11.470 line:80%
I won't bother you any longer.

00:40:10.400 --> 00:40:15.340 line:80%
[Government]

00:40:11.740 --> 00:40:14.430 line:80%
About the transfer, could you please...

00:40:14.450 --> 00:40:15.520 line:80%
Don't mention it.

00:40:16.250 --> 00:40:17.130 line:80%
Fan Daniu

00:40:17.260 --> 00:40:18.990 line:80%
has already filed the lawsuit.

00:40:19.190 --> 00:40:20.810 line:80%
The hearing will be
in 10 days at the latest.

00:40:20.810 --> 00:40:22.430 line:80%
You'd better be prepared.

00:40:24.560 --> 00:40:26.670 line:80%
[Government]

00:40:25.110 --> 00:40:26.440 line:80%
There's one more thing.

00:40:26.880 --> 00:40:28.260 line:80%
On my wedding day,

00:40:28.800 --> 00:40:31.000 line:80%
please come early for the wedding wine.

00:40:31.570 --> 00:40:33.010 line:80%
Not bad, Changyu.

00:40:33.210 --> 00:40:34.440 line:80%
You move fast.

00:40:35.020 --> 00:40:36.080 line:80%
Congratulations.

00:40:36.450 --> 00:40:37.490 line:80%
I'll definitely be there.

00:40:37.490 --> 00:40:45.020 line:80%
[Qingping County Government Office]

00:40:38.590 --> 00:40:41.100 line:80%
There's one more thing
I need to trouble you with.

00:40:41.100 --> 00:40:43.550 line:80%
My husband's money and travel permit

00:40:43.580 --> 00:40:45.390 line:80%
were all stolen by bandits.

00:40:45.490 --> 00:40:47.340 line:80%
He's marrying into my family soon.

00:40:47.340 --> 00:40:49.340 line:80%
I want to get him a new travel permit.

00:40:50.030 --> 00:40:52.090 line:80%
It coincides with the refugee roundup.

00:40:52.090 --> 00:40:53.160 line:80%
Reissuing a new travel permit

00:40:53.160 --> 00:40:54.660 line:80%
is not an easy task.

00:40:55.220 --> 00:40:57.310 line:80%
But I owe your father a debt of gratitude,

00:40:57.310 --> 00:40:59.080 line:80%
so I will definitely help you.

00:41:00.090 --> 00:41:01.220 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

00:41:01.460 --> 00:41:03.330 line:80%
Luckily,
you work at the magistrate's office.

00:41:03.330 --> 00:41:04.130 line:80%
It's nothing.

00:41:04.190 --> 00:41:05.520 line:80%
Consider it a gift.

00:41:08.260 --> 00:41:10.060 line:80%
Right. Look carefully up there.

00:41:36.730 --> 00:41:37.300 line:80%
Found it!

00:41:38.570 --> 00:41:39.400 line:80%
Come.

00:41:41.470 --> 00:41:42.090 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:41:42.480 --> 00:41:43.460 line:80%
Come!

00:41:43.770 --> 00:41:44.250 line:80%
Look.

00:41:44.920 --> 00:41:45.840 line:80%
That damn girl.

00:41:45.870 --> 00:41:47.370 line:80%
She hid it behind that "Fill Your Belly."

00:41:47.370 --> 00:41:48.970 line:80%
It was so h-hard to find it.

00:41:47.930 --> 00:41:55.760 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:41:51.050 --> 00:41:52.180 line:80%
We finally found it.

00:41:52.340 --> 00:41:52.940 line:80%
Yes.

00:41:53.500 --> 00:41:54.060 line:80%
Let's go!

00:41:54.220 --> 00:41:54.940 line:80%
Stop.

00:42:01.570 --> 00:42:02.700 line:80%
Why is there a person here?

00:42:02.700 --> 00:42:03.330 line:80%
Didn't you see him?

00:42:03.330 --> 00:42:04.860 line:80%
Didn't you see him just now?

00:42:10.160 --> 00:42:11.490 line:80%
Put down the title deed.

00:42:12.930 --> 00:42:13.620 line:80%
What?

00:42:13.930 --> 00:42:15.100 line:80%
I said,

00:42:15.710 --> 00:42:17.340 line:80%
leave the title deed,

00:42:18.260 --> 00:42:19.890 line:80%
and I'll let you go.

00:42:22.610 --> 00:42:23.790 line:80%
A man with three legs—

00:42:23.790 --> 00:42:24.890 line:80%
he sure is arrogant.

00:42:24.890 --> 00:42:26.670 line:80%
He is a cripple.

00:42:26.700 --> 00:42:28.030 line:80%
You're a cripple.

00:42:28.100 --> 00:42:29.580 line:80%
You can't even stand up.

00:42:29.980 --> 00:42:31.180 line:80%
And you want to fight?

00:42:32.340 --> 00:42:34.970 line:80%
Do you believe
I'll break your good leg too?

00:42:35.290 --> 00:42:36.260 line:80%
Try me.